# 🗺️ Project Roadmap

This roadmap outlines the planned improvements and future enhancements for the Weather & Time Detection AI Agent. The goal is to gradually transform the project into a more capable, scalable, and production-ready AI assistant.

---

# Current Version (v1.0)

## ✅ Completed Features

- AI-powered Weather Detection
- AI-powered Time Detection
- Google Agent Development Kit (ADK) Integration
- Gemini API Integration
- Tool Calling
- Modular Python Architecture
- Environment Variable Support
- Project Documentation
- GitHub Repository Setup

